name: MonsterPunks Half-year Anniversary
description:
Hello, World! It happened six months ago. And since then, I've been creating monsters almost every day. Has my life changed? Definitely. I want to thank every person who supported me, those, who were with me from the beginning, and, of course, every monster owner. I wouldn't go that far without your support! Thank you!
Everyone is welcome to our Monster Fam!
